01:00:05,135 --> 01:00:07,221
All right...

400
01:00:11,433 --> 01:00:14,604
Come on, let's go.

401
01:00:41,427 --> 01:00:45,724
Come on, who's first?

402
01:00:47,726 --> 01:00:51,187
Get out of there, Charlie.

403
01:00:58,696 --> 01:01:01,323
Get out of there.

404
01:01:08,665 --> 01:01:11,210
Jesus Christ!

405
01:01:15,299 --> 01:01:18,260
